TRAMP Real-time Application Mobility Platform
http://tramp-project.org/

=====INTRODUCTION===============================================================

This package contains the files for the TRAMP Data Exchanger, including the
TRAMP daemon, the shared library and sample application components. The
framework allows distributed application components to share data efficiently.

=====FILES======================================================================

AUTHORS          - List of authors...
README           - This file...
Makefile         - Makefile for GNU make utility. Run "make help" for more info!
shm_clear.sh     - Script for manipulating shared memory. Used for debugging.

app_producer.c   - Part 1 of 2 of the sample application. Inputs data.
app_consumer.c   - Part 2 of 2 of the sample application. Outputs data.

libtramp.h       - Header file for the shared library used by the applications.
libtramp.c       - Implementation of the shared library.

trampd.h         - Header file for the TRAMP daemon responsible for sockets etc.
trampd.c         - Implementation of the TRAMP daemon.

my-devices.cache - List of devices the TRAMP daemon uses for bootstrapping.

================================================================================
